Revision history for perl module C::Utility

0.013 2018-11-13

* Bug fix in read_includes (return value no longer contains #include)

0.012 2018-09-01

* Bug fixes in linein/lineout
* Extended examples of use of linein/lineout in documentation

0.011 2018-09-01

* Use more of C::Tokenize's regexes instead of duplicating
* Document the functions better

0.010 2018-08-31

* Better line numbering in lineout and linein
* Dependency on Text::LineNumber introduced

0.009 2018-03-27

* Dependency bug fix

0.008 2018-03-27

* Add "read_includes" function

0.007 2017-10-13

* Documentation

0.006 2017-02-09

* Documentation
* hash_to_c_file returns the value of the generated .h file
* New function "stamp_file"

0.005 2014-02-26

* Add "make-c-text" executable to distribution.

0.004 2013-12-13

* Add "remove_quotes" function.

0.003 2013-11-27

* Use "croak" instead of "die" for errors.
* Add "ch_files" function.
* Add "Changes".

0.002 2012-04-19

* Add "DESCRIPTION" section to documentation.
* Better documentation.

0.001 2012-04-14

